
  Honedge    Steel Type Pokémon

  Apparently this Pokémon is born 
  when a departed spirit inhabits 
  a sword.  It attaches itself 
  to people and drinks their life 
  force. 
	   Evolution Chain
  Honedge ► Doublade ► Aegislash

